Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:01.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:07.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:11.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 当猫耳是藤原书记时那四宫就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:15.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你带来的时间原本就只有四宫与猫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:23.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,猫耳与少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,互惠共生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:33.10,Kaguya_zw,,0,0,0,,这世上存在着生来就注定相配的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:34.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三叶草和蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,鳄鱼与蜂鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛油果与酱油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:40.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然后便是…猫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数人类都喜爱猫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:48.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而后在此 有四宫辉夜这一容貌端庄的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:52.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这两种存在的相适性在他眼中又是如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:56.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱死了
