Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎会真的需要Cosplay吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.00,Kaguya_hm_cuyasong,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50\c&H2F2C2D&\3c&HF0F0F0&\fad(150,0)}法国交换留学生欢迎会日程表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.49,0:02:32.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:35.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法国可是仅次于日本的Cosplay大国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Cosplay是不需要语言交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:40.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想要超越语言限制增进友谊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比这更好的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:45.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:48.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:48.99,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\an8\fs75\c&H0405BF&\3c&HF3F3EF&}Mariage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.84,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,可 可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 一看四宫我的表情就僵硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看点正常的东西然后冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,表情好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反应不大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我还是不太适合这类装扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:17.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还是让藤原那样可爱的女孩子戴比较合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:16.33,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长你也干脆一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:23.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么说呢 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太多余了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得那么一针见血 你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本就不适合这种装扮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.17,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord3\an8\fs75\c&H0405BF&\3c&HF3F3EF&}Mariage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 明明会长只是戴上了猫耳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说别人 这对辉夜而言是最棒的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:54.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 嘴角上扬停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:58.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会暴露我觉得会长很可爱的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:00.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗 四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,技能「咬舌头」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而这也做不到完美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还是留下了模棱两可的笑意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我的猫耳有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你的猫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:27.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可真适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:28.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,视人为蝼蚁的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是我是最不适合猫耳的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学 给会长拍张照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:45.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可得把会长的这个样子永远存留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:46.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是威胁的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她打算将来留下证据然后用来威胁我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,来 辉夜同学也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:56.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫也要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果拍了照片 我的弱点就被掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:05.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 同时我能合法地获得这个可爱存在的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,利益与损失相等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,快点拍吧 藤原书记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银选择向可爱屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他作出了平时绝不会下的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,用 用那个叫4K的东西照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,凑近了看更可爱了啊可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我脸上的肌肉都要僵硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他还真是适合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我又要咧嘴笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,两位 能不能笑得开心一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:42.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:42.99,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想更近地欣赏这份可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:49.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要在更近的距离内把这烙印在眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你们在互瞪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩如果要吵架的话 这个就没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是的 到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像是被什么附身了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,猫耳太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.76,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,猫耳太可怕了
