Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,切克闹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长说先回家再讨论买东西的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:17.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长买手机的那天我们就交换了邮箱和手机号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是等了那么久都没有任何联络
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长根本不打算先发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 我很期待明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:27.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 只是想替你发一下邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能我先发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:37.08,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs75\pos(440,1046)}辉夜大小姐想要收邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐你喜欢白银会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:46.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:47.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:53.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我只是判断出他具有我缺少的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有点兴趣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:01.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小书记和白银交往了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不爽会长被藤原同学抢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说她也是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.41,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看\N活的章鱼~~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是重要的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这么在意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐 别等邮件了 打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:27.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,电…电话！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对方正等着你发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着这一瞬间的疏忽 出其不意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,疏忽…出其不意…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:37.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了是完美的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在辉夜大小理清头绪之前 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:45.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 等等 我还没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:48.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:53.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是四宫 请问是会长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御行的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:02.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…就是…会长 不对…白银呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是白银啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:08.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 御…御行呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你找我儿子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,御行 有女生打电话找你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:16.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？有女生给哥哥打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你别乱接别人电话啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:22.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 四宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:30.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想打电话和你商量一下明天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:32.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在泡澡 不过没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:43.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐你在和一个全裸的人打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.20,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,声音是不是有点不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一会儿再打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 我手机是防水的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,问题大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明天11点在八公像前面集合 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去买点日式点心再去逛一下东急手创馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就差不多这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.06,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HF3F3F3&\c&H212121&\b1\fs75\fad(300,0)}再拖一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 他刚才要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:15.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡了
