Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 第一封邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局 辉夜的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,听说涩谷站被淹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:41.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:47.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长在等我 我必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他不可能去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,中止邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但这也是四宫发的第一封邮件 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就这样也挺好
