Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:30.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家玩得尽兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.17,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫会说法语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:37.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是很擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:38.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:41.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你好大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫白银御行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:47.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是会长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:51.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是翻了翻应急手册 临时抱佛脚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Bonjour
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Merci beaucoup pour votreinvitation d' aujourd' hui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:56.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}非常感谢你今天的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,C' est nous qui vous remercions d'être venus d' aussi loin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}感谢你们的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Nous ferons toutnotre possiblepour que vous gardiez un souvenir impérissable durant votreséjour parmi nous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:08.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}在这期间 我们将尽力为您留下难忘的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Je vous remercie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,La pluparts des contenusjaponais sont focalisés surle marché domestique Le Japon n' a pas encoreétabli la fa?on de se promouvoir à I' étranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}日本的文化产物大都集中在国内市场 因此还没建立起在国外推广的途径
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Les prix montent en flèche à I' exportation,il y a aussi les problèmes des ventes au rabais des licences des images…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}出口价格暴涨 图片许可证的折扣销售也存在问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会说法语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因为妈妈以前是外交官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候就被灌输了各国语言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:27.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不会说法语的只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:35.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被发现只有我不会说法语的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本学校的学生会长居然不会说法语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:45.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Comme c' est mignon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 对心脏太不友好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:58.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:03.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得为什么我会突然委托你策划派对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:08.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须要看透你的才能是否值得我将学园托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:12.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来才是真正的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:23.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要有顾虑 全力去进攻那个叫白银御行的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法国学校学生会副会长 Beltoise Betsy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作是「舔舐伤口的剃刀」的她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:35.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在她的毒舌下没有人可以毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Bonjour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:37.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 hey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy 刚见面就使出破颜拳级别的讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接着是如同同时侮辱父母和恋人般的挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:58.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:03.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是能让六十多岁的男性痛哭流涕的人格否定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:07.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白银御行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么可怕的攻击下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还能露出这样从容的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫的话应该早就败下阵来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就像完全听不懂她说的话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:26.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的攻击居然没有效 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:31.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,Betsy向白银发起了强烈的侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:47.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 你听不懂日语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:21:01.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜向Betsy发起了电视台放送事故级别的恐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:13.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 不是的 刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我 会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的女子高中生太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:27.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,交流战 日本学校的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:36.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很瞧不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了那么不文雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直就好像以前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:47.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.52,0:21:49.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的法语是临时抱佛脚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:51.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:54.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不知道你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:59.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你是在替我打抱不平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.25,0:22:03.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:10.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长 会长的这点我很…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:16.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:20.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 这样会更在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密就是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:25.07,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不是法语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.24,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是拉丁语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:26.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局 两人均胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:29.16,Kaguya_zw,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\bord7\3c&H141414&\1a&H00&\an7\pos(466,492)\fad(600,1700)}m 0 0 l 0 500 l 250 500 l 250 0
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:29.16,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H010101&\fs65\an8\pos(646,522)\fad(600,1700)}都\N让\N对\N方\N看\N见\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:29.16,Kaguya_hm_songti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H010101&\fs65\an8\pos(546,522)\fad(600,1700)}自\N己\N的\N弱\N点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:27.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,意第绪语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:28.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,芬兰语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:29.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:42.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:42.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 现在一定怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:59.97,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:59.97,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就还能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.99,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.99,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经注意到我在用坏心眼的谋略考验他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.05,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.05,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经不能退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.88,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.88,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}让我给你设下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:19.06,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:19.06,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}来吧 掉进陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:29.12,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:29.12,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然后在最后说出那句喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:36.82,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:36.81,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 将会怎样相恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:40.71,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:40.71,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:48.32,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:48.32,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注视 我一点都不从容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:52.13,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:52.13,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我总是会颤抖着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:59.11,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:59.11,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}请带走这样不坦率的我！
